column5: Fast food restaurant offering burgers fries and classic menu items. Great for a quick meal on-the-go. Family-friendly and available for takeout and delivery.

Indulge in finger-lickin' good moments at KFC where the secret blend of 11 herbs and spices transforms every piece of chicken into a crispy golden masterpiece. From classic buckets to sandwiches KFC brings people together with every bite.

Craving bold adventurous flavors? Taco Bell serves up a fiesta of Tex-Mex delights from crunchy tacos to cheesy quesadillas and the iconic Crunchwrap Supreme. Always something to excite your taste buds.
Freshly made sandwiches and wraps with a wide variety of bread and filling options. Customizable to your preferences Subway offers healthy fast food choices for all diets.
Pizza thatâ€™s always fresh hot and delicious. Choose from a wide selection of toppings and crusts including gluten-free options. Fast delivery for pizza lovers!
Canadian-owned pizza chain offering a variety of pizzas pasta wings and sides. Known for quick delivery and custom pizza options. Perfect for every occasion!
Enjoy a unique blend of Indian and Chinese flavors at Hakka Legend. Known for its flavorful dishes and friendly service. Try their signature Hakka-style fried rice and curry chicken!
Delicious pizza made with high-quality ingredients. Fresh dough savory sauce and your choice of toppings. Takeout and delivery available for a satisfying meal.
Freedy Fazbear Pizza! Enjoy pizza and arcade games!
